ygData.messageBody:
I have a v.90 but the lines are so bad here that I cannot get a v.90
connection, If I lived 5 or 6 miles from here I could..On a plus note i was
able to get into the game for a while last night and today. Killed Broon a
few times for a little payback. Scared some lower level hi elf in an oracle
robe...she was right next to me when I cast my first spell and I was
invisable when I did it. She got even more scared when he charged me cause
he was heading right at her hehehe. Just wonder how someone lower than 26
got an oracle robe? I want one
